<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3149124" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="3"><variable id="sytextlegende"><ahelp hid=".uno:ToggleLegend">To show or hide a legend, click <emph>Legend On/Off</emph> on the <emph>Formatting</emph> bar.</ahelp>
